This antioxidant-rich blend combines wild blueberry, goji, schisandra, and elderberry to ward off free radical damage, plus fruity red hibiscus and cacao to tantalize your taste buds. Gut-balancing probiotics and digestive enzymes are at work to help your body absorb all the nutrients from your food for peak health.
